1) Copy all the Corpus text files(Heliohost, data from blogs and data from newspapers) into one folder and run:
	$ cat *txt > finalcorpus.txt
   This will merge all the data into one files

2)  Run: $ make
3)  Run: ./a.out filteredcorpus.txt 1 1 0 1 0
4)  Copy Output/finalSegmentation.txt as pranjalresult.txt
5)  Run: $ python mixtesttrain.py > pranjal.txt
6)  Run $ python stats.py

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Files:

1) Stats.py: Caluclates precison, recall and F-Score

2) filter.py:  Filters out certain special characters

3) lineremove.py: Removes blank lines

4) freqcount.py:  Finds frequency of each distinct word

5) specialremove.py: Removes words with less than 3 characters by ignoring matras
